      <EnglishText>Reid</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ガイ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guy</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>フレン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Flynn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おい、お前！
赤い髪でヘソだしとか
俺とキャラかぶらせてんじゃねぇよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, you! Redhead with an exposed midsection?
Don't you dare make your character design
exactly like mine!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>すぐに髪黒く染めて来い！
あと厚着しろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Go dye your hair black right now!
And put on more clothes.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>かぶってるって言われてもな……。
オレの方が先にやってたんだぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You say my design is exactly like yours...
but you realize I had mine done first, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うるせぇ！　関係あるか！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shut up! That doesn't matter!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>こら、ルーク。
あんまり無茶言うな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Enough, Luke.
Stop talking so recklessly.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、無茶はよくない。
たしかにヘソ部分に関しては仕方ないが
性格が違いすぎるから大丈夫だよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's right, it's not good to be reckless.
It's true his exposed midsection is similar to you,
but your personalities are quite different.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>その通りだな。　心配ないさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Exactly. It's nothing to worry about.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうそう、心配ないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yup, it's nothing to worry about.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うるせぇ！
お前もガイとかぶってんじゃねぇよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shut up! You're just trying to copy Guy!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
